org.mini2Dx.ui.element

Class TextBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mini2Dx.ui.element.UiElement
      • org.mini2Dx.ui.element.TextBox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Actionable, FlexUiElement, Hoverable

    public class TextBox
extends UiElement
implements Actionable, FlexUiElement
    A text box UiElement. Can optionally function as a password field.
